Think of the possibilities. .. to be able to reimagine this 1 bedroom Hollywood Hills Cottage off the famed Laurel Canyon. Add a bedroom and bath, do a total remodel, or a rebuild as there is ample land to be used with a good sized side yard and a bit of a backyard next to a rear hillside. Newer roof and painted exterior a few years ago. Good bones, just needs someone creative to make it a perfect pied de terre, or create something brand new.

8270 Kirkwood Dr is a house in Los Angeles, CA 90046. This 710 square foot house sits on a 2,151 square foot lot and features 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom. This house has been listed on Redfin since October 02, 2020 and is currently priced at $870,000. 8270 Kirkwood Dr was built in 1921. Based on Redfin's Los Angeles data, we estimate the home's value is $863,659, which is 0.7% less than its current list price. Comparable nearby homes include 8501 Walnut Dr, 2127 Stanley Hills Dr, and 8526 Walnut Dr N. According to Redfin's Rental Estimate, we expect that this home would rent for between $3,228 and $4,305. Nearby schools include Wonderland Avenue Elementary School, Wonderland Ave Elementary School and West Hollywood College Prep School. The closest grocery stores are Laurel Canyon Country Store, Trader Joe's and Bristol Farms Hollywood. Nearby coffee shops include Starbucks, Starbucks and The Coffee Bean and Tea Leaf. Nearby restaurants include Pace, Pink Taco and The Den of Hollywood. 8270 Kirkwood Dr is near Trebek Open Space, Wattles Garden Park and Laurel Canyon Park.
